      <para>Part I of this guide is intended to help you use
        to DarwinPorts system.  The Part II is directed towards
        users who wish to add their favorite software to DarwinPorts.
        The Part III is intended for developers interested in extending
        the DarwinPorts system.</para>

      <para>The Guide is still at an early draft stage, if you have any
	comments, corrections or (even bettter) contributions, please
	contact the OpenDarwin Documentation Project at
	<email>doc@opendarwin.org</email>.</para>
  </preface>

